The Government’s vision is to ensure access to affordable, equitable, and reliable energy sources and services to drive and secure national development, and to improve the quality of life for all of its citizens. The Government is therefore committed to:
* Facilitate the integration of renewable energy sources into the national energy mix;
* Guarantee the judicious development of the islandâs indigenous hydrocarbon resources;
* Guarantee social inclusiveness and equity to access to energy; and
* Build a more competitive, productive economy.
